cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.SY. 

This paper is about developing a domain-specific language for robot perception, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The language is designed to specify the expected result of a robot perception architecture, which involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computer vision (cs.CV) techniques. The language is also declarative and framework-independent, which could be related to machine learning (cs.LG) and systems and control (cs.SY) sub-categories.
